data.description: This 3 bedroom, 1 full/2 half bath home gives you the space you need with the added benefit of customizing to your own taste! Plenty of room for outdoor activities! Recent upgrades include fresh paint, all new toilets, brand new ROOF just put on (10/2023). Newer garage door with space for 2 vehicles. Formal dining room w/walkout to spacious deck, fenced rear yard, finished lower level, neutral dcor! Hardwood floors throughout the house except the family room (carpet) and kitchen (vinyl) floors. Fantastic location near shopping center, restaurants, parks and so much more!!!
